Name: Star Trek: Strange New Worlds
Title: Strange New Worlds
Desc: When one of Pike's officers goes missing on a secret mission, Pike comes out of self-imposed exile.
LongDescription: When one of Pike's officers goes missing while on a secret mission for Starfleet, Pike has to come out of self-imposed exile; he must navigate how to rescue his officer, while struggling with what to do with the vision of the future he's been given.
